Package: githapi
Title: User-friendly access to the GitHub API for R
Version: 1.0.1
Authors@R: person(
    "Chad", "Goymer", email = "chad.goymer@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides a suite of functions to simplify working with GitHub's 
    API. The functions are designed to be compatible with the Tidyverse.
